{"tid":1364872,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"本人謹以至誠宣誓","createTime":"2019-07-25T12:50:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T13:03:55.000Z","uid":88507,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cf316090f13eb817f1d228967230228229a59ab2","tid":1364872,"uid":88507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:50:59.000Z","msg":"以警員身分，竭誠伙拍黑社會依法治港。並依照權利至上的原則無視法律，維護權貴。不中立，不放生，並行使職權對付市民，並毫不懷疑施行西環所有命令。"},{"pid":"b45adb9fa88329884e79b4acb9db5b0ca568e5cd","tid":1364872,"uid":88507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:56:33.000Z","msg":"佢班畜牲係咪咁樣宣誓"},{"pid":"00076573082681940dbd4c9bae9b5a34162b761b","tid":1364872,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:57:38.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"0134758e31c23b8a03cdcaaa193cd44497907cd7","tid":1364872,"uid":258717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T12:57:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QcDDv2d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQcDDv2d.png&h=dbdb7595&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1cee2c57a114676029beae94b0f1b592d823c08a","tid":1364872,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:03:55.000Z","msg":"仲諗緊出唔出元朗好<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1364858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1364858</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}